      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1768792552,
      "updated": 1768792554
    },
    {
      "id": "696da1ea0000000000e4843c",
      "text": " [能ある鷹は爪を隠す]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1768792555,
      "updated": 1768792562
    },
    {
      "id": "696de7db0000000000c67fef",
      "text": " 　頭の良さの話ね",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1768810460,
      "updated": 1768810470
    },
    {
      "id": "696da1eb0000000000e4843d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1768792555,
      "updated": 1768792555
    },
    {
      "id": "696da684000000000035aec0",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1768793731,
      "updated": 1768793734
    },
    {
      "id": "696da6b00000000000c6f390",
      "text": "　仕事前睡眠時間4時間か…",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1768793776,
      "updated": 1768793796
    },
    {
      "id": "696da6bb0000000000c6f391",
      "text": "　 　コーヒー飲めばいけるな！",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1768793787,
      "updated": 1768793807
    },
    {
      "id": "696da6cc0000000000c6f392",
      "text": "　 お腹が痛い…",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1768793804,
      "updated": 1768793821
    },
    {
      "id": "696da6df0000000000c6f393",
      "text": "　 　水と胃薬飲めばいけるな！",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1768793822,
      "updated": 1768793839
    },
    {
      "id": "696da6ef0000000000c6f394",
      "text": "　 慣れって怖い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1768793839,
      "updated": 1768793849
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4cd740000000000432854",
      "text": "　[頭の良さ]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776602483,
      "updated": 1776602490
    },
    {
      "id": "696db7950000000000950b73",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1768798101,
      "updated": 1768798101
    },
    {
      "id": "696db7950000000000950b74",
      "text": " [TablePlus]かなり良い",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1768798102,
      "updated": 1768819503
    },
    {
      "id": "696db79d0000000000950b75",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1768798109,
      "updated": 1768798109
    },
    {
      "id": "696db79d0000000000950b76",
      "text": "[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1768798109,
      "updated": 1768800246
    },
    {
      "id": "696dbff600000000005411af",
      "text": " 東京の嫌なところ: 人の吐瀉物をちょくちょく目にすること",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1768800247,
      "updated": 1768800309
    },
    {
      "id": "696dc1dc00000000005411b1",
      "text": "  東京のというより都会のか",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1768800733,
      "updated": 1768800749
    },
    {
      "id": "696dcf9d00000000009b89e5",
      "text": "  金曜日の電車[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1768804254,
      "updated": 1768804260
    },
    {
      "id": "696dd72f000000000014cb3f",
      "text": "\t\t繁華街だとよく見る光景[カイト.icon]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1768806192,
      "updated": 1768806847
    },
    {
      "id": "696e03f0000000000033aaa6",
      "text": "\t\t道の端をぼーっと歩いていると踏むので道の真ん中を歩く[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1768817649,
      "updated": 1768817677
    },
    {
      "id": "696f4b570000000000cb0a1e",
      "text": "\t\tこないだ商業ビルのエレベーターに乗ろうとしたらド真ん中に人糞が放置されてた[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1768901466,
      "updated": 1768901564
    },
    {
      "id": "696e10af0000000000d3df73",
      "text": "\t斜め上を行く川崎:",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1768820912,
      "updated": 1768820928
    },
    {
      "id": "696e10c00000000000d3df74",
      "text": "\t [築浅の川崎市役所本庁舎、地下駐車場に嘔吐や排泄 「多すぎて分からない」運営側の声も：東京新聞デジタル https://www.tokyo-np.co.jp/article/462085]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1768820928,
      "updated": 1768820999
    },
    {
      "id": "696dcfa400000000009b89e6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1768804260,
      "updated": 1768804261
    },
    {
      "id": "696dcfa400000000009b89e7",
      "text": "[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1768804261,
      "updated": 1768804303
    },
    {
      "id": "696dcfcf0000000000e9da95",
      "text": " 全てはAIの前に等しく無力モードに入っている",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1768804304,
      "updated": 1768804322
    },
    {
      "id": "696e03840000000000f27cf4",
      "text": " [insta360]のAI動画編集、手軽で良い",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1768817541,
      "updated": 1776602596
    },
    {
      "id": "696e01ed00000000005fc5b2",
      "text": "　　vlogは編集コストを低くしたい",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1768817399,
      "updated": 1768817584
    },
    {
      "id": "696e03ad0000000000f27cf6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1768817581,
      "updated": 1768817581
    },
    {
      "id": "696ddffd0000000000b51d9e",
      "text": "[綾坂こと.icon]",
      "userId": "62919f6444e78d001d73e522",
      "created": 1768808446,
      "updated": 1768808447
    },
    {
      "id": "696ddfff0000000000b51d9f",
      "text": " [Gemini]君、音声概要生成しても音声ファイルのローディングが終わらずに再生できない　なぜ",
      "userId": "62919f6444e78d001d73e522",
